headline.print_headline: Australia RBA Wary of Stoking House Prices With Lower Rates
headline.main: Australia RBA Wary of Stoking House Prices With Lower Rates

lead_paragraph: Australia's top central banker on Wednesday signalled further cuts in interest rates were unlikely as it would be "unwise" to risk further inflating already high house prices.
